thread.title: BRIEF-Engie To Help Develop Nine Subsidy-Free Farms in Spain

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Engie To Help Develop Nine Subsidy-Free Farms in Spain

organizations.name: brief-engie to help develop nine subsidy-free farms

text:
May 23 (Reuters) - Engie Sa:
* SAYS SIGNED WITH FORESTALIA, GENERAL ELECTRIC AND MIROVA AN INNOVATIVE AGREEMENT TO DEVELOP NINE SUBSIDY-FREE WIND FARMS WITH A TOTAL CAPACITY OF 300 MW AWARDED AT SPANISH RENEWABLE GENERATION AUCTION IN 2016
* SAYS SHAREHOLDERS OF THE PROJECT ARE MIROVA (51%), GENERAL ELECTRIC (25%), ENGIE (15%) AND FORESTALIA (9%), THE TOTAL INVESTMENT OF THE PROJECT WILL REACH 300 MILLION EUR Further company coverage:
